data.title: The Fifth Head Of Cerberus Episodes
data.meta_description: Podcast episodes on the topic of The Fifth Head of Cerberus from Alzabo Soup.
data.text:
Alzabo Soup is the podcast where we literally become our favorite authors by devouring portions of their brains. We analyze engrossing speculative fiction with a chapter-by-chapter focus on acclaimed author Gene Wolfe. We update weekly on Fridays.

We are currently covering The Book of the Short Sun by Gene Wolfe.
